quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,"Omeo laza tsara aho amin’ireo taranaka amam-para any aoriana."
  26,85,"Ary ataovy an’isan’ireo mpandova ny Paradisan’ny «Na’ìm» (fahafinaretana) aho."
  26,86,"Ary mamelà ny heloky ny raiko, satria izy dia tena anisan’ireo very lalana."
  26,87,"Ary aza alaina baraka aho amin’ny andro hampitsanganana ireo maty."
  26,88,"Amin’ny andro izay tsy hitera-boka-tsoa, na ny harena na ny zanaka."
  26,89,"Afa-tsy izay tonga eo anatrehan’I Allah miaraka amin’ny fo madio."
  26,90,"Ary hampanatonina ny Paradisa, ho an’ireo nanam-patahorana."
  26,91,"Ary haseho ny afobe, ho an’ireo very lalana."
  26,92,"Ary ho tenenina amin’izy ireo hoe : “Aiza ireo izay notompoinareo?""
  26,93,"Ankoatr’I Allah ? Moa ve manavotra anareo izy ireo ? Sa afaka manavotra ny tenany ve izy ireo ?"
  26,94,"Ary hatsipy hifangaro ao izy ireo, sy ireo very lalana."
  26,95,"Toy izany koa ireo miaramilan’i Iblisa rehetra."
  26,96,"Hiteny izy ireo ao, sady mifanditra :"
  26,97,"Mianiana amin’I Allah izahay fa tena ao anatin’ny fahaverezana miharihary tokoa."
  26,98,"Raha nampitovy anareo tamin’ny Tompon’izao Tontolo izao izahay !"
  26,99,"Ary tsy nisy namery lalana anay afa-tsy ireo mpanao heloka bevava !"
  26,100,"Ary tsy manana mpanelanelana izahay."
  26,101,"Na sakaiza mafana fo !"
  26,102,"Raha nanana fahafahana miverina izahay dia ho anisan’ireo mpino !"
  26,103,"Marina fa amin’izany dia misy fahagagana tokoa, nefa ny ankamaroan’izy ireo dia tsy mpino."
  26,104,"Ary marina fa ny Tomponao, Izy no ilay Tsitoha, ilay be indrafo."
  26,105,"Nilaza ireo Iraka ho mpandainga ny vahoakan’i Noa."
  26,106,"Rehefa niteny tamin’izy ireo i Noa, rahalahin’izy ireo, hoe : “Tsy matahotra (an’I Allah) ve ianareo ?"
  26,107,"Izaho dia Iraka mendri-pitokisana ho anareo !"
  26,108,"Ary matahora an’I Allah àry ianareo, ary ankatoavy aho."
  26,109,"Ary tsy mangataka tambiny aminareo aho momba izany, tsy mila tambiny aho afa-tsy avy amin’ny Tompon’izao tontolo izao."
  26,110,"Ary matahora an’I Allah àry ianareo, ary mankatoava ahy."
  26,111,"Niteny izy ireo hoe : “Moa ve hino anao izahay, nefa ireny olona ambany saranga indrindra ireny no manaraka anao ?”"